title: I'll Bring the Spaghetti-Os
description: Jay sits down with Sam Kauffman and Justin Meeks and tries to make sense of this hot mess of an election season. Is Clinton the leader we need (even if nobody really wants her), or should we all be getting ready for the Trumpocalypse?

title: What Would Tobias Do?
description: David Allen and Zach Buhrer of Shreveport have been staying with Jay for nearly a week, without so much as an apology for the funky smell they left in his living room. They discuss it all over breakfast.

title: I Have a Level 50 Lucario! Yay!
description: A quick episode in which humble guitarist Robert Kemper and returning comedian Andrew Rose nerd out with Jay over Pokemon and butcher a game of Cards Against Humanity.

title: I Was Gonna Wear Pants, But... Ughh
description: Jay is joined by Devincey Moore, Desiree Newton and travelling guest Irene Tu, who flew all the way out from San Fransisco to encounter roaches during this recording. She was a little freaked out, it seems.

title: Dasswhatimtalgginabowd
description: Jose Sarduy and Bob Khosravi sit down with Jay to talk comedy shop, what it means to be true to your own voice onstage, being unique, and how much the Batman vs Superman movie is probably gonna suck.
